dvbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1516","checkdouble":"191809"},{"date":"06:25 23/07","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 ti\u1ebfn c\u1eed nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 mang v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c danh hi\u1ec7u cho Liverpool","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/11/5/mu-chi-30-trieu-bang-cho-trung-ve-cua-atletico.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Liverpool \u0111ang nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi trung v\u1ec7 Domagoj Vida c\u1ee7a Besiktas. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u1ef1u h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Steve Nicol tin r\u1eb1ng Liverpool c\u1ea7n mua Diego Godin c\u1ee7a Atletico Madrid nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Liverpool \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft Vida</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, Domagoj Vida l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1eaft x\u00edch c\u1ee7a \u0110T Croatia ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t hay. Anh g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00f9ng Balkan l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede \u0111\u00f3, Vida \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ee3p c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Dejan Lovren tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1eb7p trung v\u1ec7 v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc v\u00e0 \u0103n \u00fd. Liverpool hi\u1ec7n c\u0169ng \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n h\u1ecd t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p. Ngo\u00e0i ra, nh\u1eefng Everton v\u00e0 West Ham c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00e1 v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng Anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool c\u1ea7n mua Diego Godin c\u1ee7a Atletico h\u01a1n Vida h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Liverpool c\u1ea7n mua Diego Godin c\u1ee7a Atletico h\u01a1n Vida h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/Liverpool-can-mua-Diego-Godin-cua-Atletico-hon-Vida-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Liverpool \u0111ang \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft Vida</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 khuy\u00ean mua Godin</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLiverpool c\u1ea7n mua Diego Godin c\u1ee7a Atletico Madrid nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n l\u00e0 Vida. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean t\u1edbi t\u1eeb c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Steve Nicol d\u00e0nh cho l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u00edch vi\u1ec7c Liverpool chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Vida\u201d, Nicols n\u00f3i v\u1edbi ESPN. \u201cN\u1ebfu t\u00f4i l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi trong cu\u1ed9c, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn Atletico v\u00e0 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng mang v\u1ec1 Godin. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh \u1edf h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"trung ve Godin\" title=\"trung ve Godin\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/11/5/mu-chi-30-trieu-bang-cho-trung-ve-cua-atletico.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Liverpool c\u1ea7n mua Diego Godin nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi cho r\u1eb1ng t\u1edbi Liverpool thay v\u00ec \u1edf l\u1ea1i Atletico c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00f9i c\u1ee7a Godin. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Nicol l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cAtletico \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i t\u1edbi chung k\u1ebft Champions League 2 m\u00f9a g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y song \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ea5u ch\u1ed1t. Atletico \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ea5y l\u1ea7n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ch\u00e2u \u00c2u? Ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 con s\u1ed1 0. C\u00f2n Liverpool? H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 5 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u0103ng quang. V\u00ec v\u1eady, gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00f9i.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng 4 t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Sau Fabinho, Naby Keita v\u00e0 Xherdan Shaqiri, Alisson c\u0169ng m\u1edbi n\u1ed1i g\u00f3t t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Anfield v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 67 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Liverpool tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/matip-quyet-canh-tranh-suat-da-chinh-tai-liverpool-172-191801.html\">Matip quy\u1ebft c\u1ea1nh tranh su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i Liverpool</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-noi-ve-phat-bieu-mu-172-191769.html\">Klopp: MU m\u1eb7c x\u00e1c Liverpool, c\u00f2n Liverpool m\u1eb7c x\u00e1c th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-dau-hieu-cho-thay-liverpool-sap-chia-tay-danny-ings-172-191735.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! D\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u cho th\u1ea5y Liverpool s\u1eafp chia tay Danny Ings</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/keita-toi-luon-tuong-tuong-minh-se-tro-thanh-gerrard-172-191724.html\">Keita: T\u00f4i lu\u00f4n t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh Gerrard</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/totti-liverpool-da-dua-ra-loi-de-nghi-khong-the-tu-choi-o-vu-alisson-184-191716.html\">Totti: Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i \u1edf v\u1ee5 Alisson</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1515","checkdouble":"191810"},{"date":"06:51 23/07","title":"Sao Man City ghen t\u1ecb v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/23/sao-man-city-ghen-ti-voi-nhung-nha-vo-dich-the-gioi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Aymeric Laporte ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Ph\u00e1p. Trung v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y ghen t\u1ecb v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Les Bleus khi b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, \u0110T Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng. H\u1ecd ti\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t m\u1ea1ch t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i n\u1ed1t Croatia \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u0103ng quang. Sau 20 n\u0103m, Les Bleus l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ai c\u0169ng vui v\u1ebb v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p. Aymeric Laporte l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong \u0111\u00f3. Trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Man City \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Didier Deschamps g\u1ecdi v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 d\u00f9 c\u00f3 tham gia m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Aymeric Laporte ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Ph\u00e1p m\u1edbi v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch WC 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Aymeric Laporte ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Ph\u00e1p m\u1edbi v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch WC 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/Aymeric-Laporte-phat-bieu-ve-DT-Phap-moi-vo-dich-WC-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 \u0111\u1ea7y x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>C\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y ghen t\u1ecb</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 vi\u1ec7c, Laporte cho bi\u1ebft th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn nh\u00ecn c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 \u0111\u0103ng quang World Cup 2018. \u201cC\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ghen t\u1ecb, th\u00e0nh th\u1eadt m\u00e0 n\u00f3i\u201d, Laporte ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Ph\u00e1p v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean. \u201cQuy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a ra v\u00e0 b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn ch\u00fang. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn h\u01a1i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham gia. \u0110\u00f3 v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a h\u00e8 vui v\u1ebb nh\u01b0 th\u01b0\u1eddng. C\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ni\u1ec1m vui c\u00f9ng gia \u0111\u00ecnh v\u00e0 b\u1ea1n b\u00e8 sau khi tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"trung ve Aymeric Laporte\" title=\"trung ve Aymeric Laporte\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/23/trung-ve-Aymeric-Laporte.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Laporte ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 ghen t\u1ecb</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nLaporte hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Man City sau khi c\u00f9ng h\u1ecd gi\u00e0nh c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap t\u1ea1i Premier League v\u00e0 c\u00fap Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc. \u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 6 th\u00e1ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y\u201d, c\u1ef1u h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Athletic Bilbao n\u00f3i. \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi tr\u1ecdng t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c r\u00e8n luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean v\u00e0 khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c gi\u00e0nh c\u00e1c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hy v\u1ecdng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh v\u00e0 t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cPep Guardiola l\u00e0 HLV gi\u1ecfi nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y lu\u00f4n t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch gi\u00fap t\u00f4i ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n khi thi \u0111\u1ea5u. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y lu\u00f4n \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi cao, nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng lo ng\u1ea1i. Phong c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Pep khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa. T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y giao cho. Chuy\u1ec3n sang Man City l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Man City tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hart-muon-roi-man-city-de-cuu-van-su-nghiep-172-191782.html\">C\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng r\u1eddi Man City \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ee9u v\u00e3n s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mahrez-hai-long-voi-man-ra-mat-man-city-172-191771.html\">Mahrez h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft Man City</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/guardiola-phan-tich-cac-sao-mai-man-city-trong-tran-thua-dortmund-172-191742.html\">Guardiola ph\u00e2n t\u00edch c\u00e1c sao mai Man City trong tr\u1eadn thua Dortmund</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/guardiola-hai-long-voi-mahrez-172-191733.html\">Man City th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, Guardiola v\u1eabn h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u00ec m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pep-guardiola-dong-vien-sao-man-city-sau-cu-soc-world-cup-172-191693.html\">Pep Guardiola \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean sao Man City sau c\u00fa s\u1ed1c World Cup</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1514","checkdouble":"191812"},{"date":"14:48 22/07","title":"C\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng r\u1eddi Man City \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ee9u v\u00e3n s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/22/hart-muon-roi-man-city-de-cuu-van-su-nghiep.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Joe Hart mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Man City \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ee9u v\u00e3n s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 31 tu\u1ed5i m\u1edbi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i N\u1eeda xanh th\u00e0nh Manchester sau qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i Torino v\u00e0 West Ham.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Hart mi\u1ec5n c\u01b0\u1ee1ng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Man City</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJoe Hart gia nh\u1eadp Man City n\u0103m 2006 t\u1eeb CLB qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 Shrewsbury Town. Anh t\u1eebng l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh The Citizens gi\u00e0nh 2 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League, 1 c\u00fap FA v\u00e0 2 c\u00fap Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb sau khi HLV Pep Guardiola l\u00ean ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n Man City \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a 2016/17, Hart kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh bi\u1ebft d\u00f9ng ch\u00e2n ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf ph\u00eda sau v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 phong c\u00e1ch s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a c\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n Man xanh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Joe Hart mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Man City \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ee9u v\u00e3n s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Joe Hart mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Man City \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ee9u v\u00e3n s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/17/Joe-Hart-muon-roi-Man-City-de-cuu-van-su-nghiep-hinh-anh.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Joe Hart kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u t\u1ea1i West Ham</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHart b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t sang Torino v\u00e0 West Ham d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n song \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng t\u00e1i hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec9nh cao. H\u1ebft m\u00f9a 2017/18, West Ham quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng mua \u0111\u1ee9t v\u00e0 bu\u1ed9c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i ph\u1ea3i quay l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Etihad.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ch\u01b0a b\u1ecf \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh ra \u0111i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJoe Hart c\u0169ng c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch sang M\u1ef9 du \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Man City h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Anh m\u1edbi c\u00f3 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean cho The Citizens t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2016 trong tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi Borussia Dortmund khi v\u00e0o s\u00e2n thay Claudio Bravo \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p 2.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"thu mon Hart\" title=\"thu mon Hart\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/22/hart-muon-roi-man-city-de-cuu-van-su-nghiep.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Hart mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Man City \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ee9u v\u00e3n s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 v\u1eady, \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a Joe Hart mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Man City \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ee9u v\u00e3n s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nguy\u00ean. \u201cT\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00e2u d\u00e0i cho m\u1ed9t CLB, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean\u201d, anh n\u00f3i. \u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 trong 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i qua b\u1edfi c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 World Cup, t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i v\u1ecb th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p cao nh\u1ea5t trong m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u trong c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. T\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng \u1edf m\u1ed9t CLB v\u00e0 t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng l\u00e2u d\u00e0i.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Man City v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n mu\u1ed1n thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n. T\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed5i kh\u00e1c v\u00e0 t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n. Th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n khi b\u1ea1n b\u1ecb \u0111em cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t khi b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb m\u00e0 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Man City tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-city-len-ke-hoach-chia-tay-sterling-172-191666.html\">Man City l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chia tay c\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-city-bo-cuoc-vu-mateo-kovacic-172-191406.html\">\u0110\u1ea1i gia \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 b\u1ecf cu\u1ed9c v\u1ee5 Mateo Kovacic</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/vua-sang-man-city-bom-tan-mahrez-da-no-tung-troi-421-191068.html\">V\u1eeba sang Man City, bom t\u1ea5n Mahrez \u0111\u00e3 \u201cn\u1ed5\u201d tung tr\u1eddi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/bom-tan-60-trieu-bang-riyad-mahrez-cua-man-city-khung-khiep-co-nao-172-191050.html\">\u201cBom t\u1ea5n\u201d 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng Riyad Mahrez c\u1ee7a Man City kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp c\u1ee1 n\u00e0o?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-city-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-mahrez-172-190895.html\">Man City CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1513","checkdouble":"191782"},{"date":"15:11 22/07","title":"T\u1edbi Barca, t\u00e2n binh 36 tri\u1ec7u Euro h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac b\u1edfi \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/22/lenglet-phat-bieu-sau-khi-toi-barca.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Clement Lenglet ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau khi t\u1edbi Barca. Trung v\u1ec7 23 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1ea5t vui v\u00ec t\u1eeb gi\u1edd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi Lionel Messi v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Blaugrana.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Lenglet gia nh\u1eadp Barca</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng n\u00e0y, Clement Lenglet \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng gia nh\u1eadp Barcelona v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 36 tri\u1ec7u Euro t\u1eeb Sevilla. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c nh\u1eefng Yerry Mina hay Thomas Vermaelen g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi ra s\u00e2n, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi trung v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nLenglet gia nh\u1eadp Sevilla \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2017 t\u1eeb Nancy v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 ch\u1ec9 5 tri\u1ec7u Euro. 1 n\u0103m r\u01b0\u1ee1i tr\u00f4i qua, gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a anh \u0111\u00e3 t\u0103ng l\u00ean h\u01a1n 7 l\u1ea7n v\u00e0 v\u1ecb th\u1ebf trong l\u00e0ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u0169ng kh\u00e1c. Lenglet gi\u1edd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb gi\u00e0u tri\u1ec3n v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Clement Lenglet ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau khi t\u1edbi Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Clement Lenglet ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau khi t\u1edbi Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/9/Clement-Lenglet-phat-bieu-sau-khi-toi-Barca-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Lenglet gia nh\u1eadp Barca t\u1eeb Sevilla</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nLenglet ti\u1ebfp b\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng Dani Alves, Seydou Keita v\u00e0 Adriano chuy\u1ec3n t\u1eeb Sevilla t\u1edbi Barca trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m qua. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft, anh s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 d\u1ef1 ph\u00f2ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i trung v\u1ec7 Gerard Pique v\u00e0 Samuel Umtiti.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>H\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u00ec m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft Barca, Lenglet b\u00e0y t\u1ecf ni\u1ec1m vui khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea1i CLB, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 Lionel Messi. \u201cT\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y, b\u1edfi t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi h\u1ecd\u201d, Lenglet ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau khi t\u1edbi Barca m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch vui v\u1ebb.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"trung ve Lenglet\" title=\"trung ve Lenglet\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/22/lenglet-phat-bieu-sau-khi-toi-barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Lenglet ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau khi t\u1edbi Barca r\u1eb1ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Messi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cMessi l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hay nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Anh \u1ea5y d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 l\u00fac n\u00e0o \u1edf b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch n\u00e0o. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n g\u1eb7p may, thi tho\u1ea3ng b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n Messi, nh\u01b0ng m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gieo s\u1ea7u cho b\u1ea1n.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nLenglet hy v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1edbm th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng \u1edf Barca. Anh tin r\u1eb1ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng t\u1ea7m h\u01a1n n\u1eefa t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y. \u201cKhi b\u1ea1n ch\u01a1i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi, s\u1ef1 th\u00edch nghi s\u1ebd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat. \u1ede \u0111\u00e2y, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p cao nh\u1ea5t\u201d, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 n\u00f3i th\u00eam.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTri\u1ebft l\u00fd c\u1ee7a Barca l\u00e0 tri\u1ec3n khai b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 CLB duy nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi ch\u01a1i v\u1edbi phong c\u00e1ch n\u00e0y. M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u n\u00f3i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i r\u1eb1ng Barcelona l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 \u0111\u00e1ng kinh ng\u1ea1c th\u1ebf n\u00e0o, v\u00e0 khi t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i.\u201d<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/everton-muon-mua-digne-gia-22-trieu-bang-172-191729.html\">\u201cH\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i\u201d Barca \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi mua v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/keita-toi-tu-choi-bayern-va-barca-de-den-liverpool-172-191715.html\">Keita: T\u00f4i t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Bayern v\u00e0 Barca \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn Liverpool</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/gui-de-nghi-lan-3-barca-quyet-mua-ngoi-sao-cua-chelsea-187-191704.html\">G\u1eedi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb l\u1ea7n 3, Barca quy\u1ebft mua ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-quan-tam-toi-jasper-cillessen-172-191681.html\">S\u1ee3 Real 'c\u01b0\u1edbp' ng\u01b0\u1eddi, Chelsea v\u1ed9i v\u00e3 h\u1ecfi mua sao Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/lucas-digne-chuan-bi-cap-ben-ngoai-hang-anh-172-191654.html\">H\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i Barca chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1512","checkdouble":"191783"},{"date":"14:37 22/07","title":"HLV H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 t\u1ef1 tin sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Thanh H\u00f3a","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/3/hlv-ha-noi-tuyen-bo-tu-tin-sau-tran-thang-thanh-hoa.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Pickford v\u00e0 Butland. H\u1ecd tin r\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c thay th\u1ebf th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Courtois r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Courtois s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Chelsea</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Thibaut Courtois v\u1edbi Chelsea ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m n\u1eefa l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1o h\u1ea1n. Nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 26 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a The Blues \u0111ang \u0111i v\u00e0o ng\u00f5 c\u1ee5t. T\u1eeb l\u00e2u, Courtois \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Madrid, n\u01a1i hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi con c\u1ee7a anh v\u1eabn sinh s\u1ed1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau World Cup 2018, Courtois c\u00e0ng mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 T\u00e2y Ban Nha h\u01a1n. \u1ede \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea1i gia \u0111ang ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n anh \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 Real Madrid. Los Blancos r\u1ea5t ch\u00fa \u00fd t\u1edbi t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Pickford v\u00e0 Butland thay Courtois h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Pickford v\u00e0 Butland thay Courtois h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/Chelsea-muon-mua-Pickford-va-Butland-thay-Courtois-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Courtois nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng r\u1eddi Chelsea</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110i\u1ec1u duy nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00edu k\u00e9o Courtois \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea l\u00e0 m\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3i ng\u1ed9 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, anh mu\u1ed1n 300 ngh\u00ecn b\u1ea3ng/ tu\u1ea7n trong h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi song CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 200 ngh\u00ecn b\u1ea3ng/ tu\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>The Blues t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBan \u0111\u1ea7u, Chelsea nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi Alisson thay Courtois. Nh\u01b0ng sau khi th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool, k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i. Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Pickford v\u00e0 Butland, 2 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Anh m\u1edbi tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"2 thu mon tuyen Anh Butland Pickford\" title=\"2 thu mon tuyen Anh Butland Pickford\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/22/2-thu-mon-tuyen-Anh-Butland-Pickford.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Pickford v\u00e0 Butland</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u01b0a khi n\u00e0o Jordan Pickford \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao nh\u01b0 b\u00e2y gi\u1edd. M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n 24 tu\u1ed5i t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 khi\u1ebfn m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a anh t\u0103ng l\u00ean 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Hi\u1ec7n ch\u01b0a r\u00f5 Pickford c\u00f3 mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Everton ch\u1ec9 sau 1 n\u0103m gia nh\u1eadp hay kh\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a Jack Butland l\u1ea1i thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u. CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n Stoke City c\u1ee7a anh m\u1edbi xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1edbi Chelsea. S\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 The Blues c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 25 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-nang-gia-hoi-mua-sao-khung-juventus-len-53-trieu-bang-172-191762.html\">Chelsea n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua sao kh\u1ee7ng Juventus l\u00ean 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/atletico-muon-co-giroud-tu-chelsea-172-191744.html\">L\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n CLB mu\u1ed1n thanh l\u00fd Giroud \u201cgi\u00fap\u201d Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/jeremie-boga-roi-chelsea-toi-sassuolo-172-191736.html\">T\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Chelsea \u0111\u1ebfn Serie A ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/100-golovin-cap-ben-chelsea-o-he-2018-172-191734.html\">100% Golovin c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Chelsea \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-bi-mat-dam-phan-mua-higuain-172-191728.html\">Chelsea b\u00ed m\u1eadt \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o m\u1edbi thay Morata</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1511","checkdouble":"191784"},{"date":"14:51 22/07","title":"L\u0110B\u0110 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 AFC n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i ASIAD?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/ldbd-chau-a-afc-noi-gi-ve-kha-nang-boc-tham-lai-asiad.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u AFC, T\u1ed5ng th\u01b0 k\u00fd Windsor John Paul kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng can thi\u1ec7p v\u00e0o quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018.\r\n\r\n</h2><h2>AFC\u00a0<span style=\"text-align: justify;\">kh\u00f4ng can thi\u1ec7p vi\u1ec7c b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i ASIAD\u00a0</span></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb, sau khi hai qu\u1ed1c gia UAE v\u00e0 Palestine g\u1eedi ki\u1ebfn ngh\u1ecb v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham d\u1ef1 m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c s\u1ebd b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nhi\u1ec1u \u00fd ki\u1ebfn cho r\u1eb1ng L\u0110B\u0110 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 AFC \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ed1i th\u00fac n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i c\u00e1c b\u1ea3ng m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa nh\u01b0ng n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 v\u1eabn \u0111ang ph\u00e2n v\u00e2n v\u1ec1 h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y, \u00f4ng Windsor John Paul\u00a0- T\u1ed5ng th\u01b0 k\u00fd\u00a0AFC kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng hay bi\u1ebft g\u00ec v\u1ec1 r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra \u1edf m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018.\u00a0<o:p></o:p>\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng can thi\u1ec7p vi\u1ec7c b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i\u201d - \u00d4ng Datuk Windsor John Paul\u00a0 chia s\u1ebb. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb n\u00e0y n\u00f3i th\u00eam: \"Th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, \u1ee6y ban Olympic ch\u00e2u \u00c1 (OCA) v\u00e0 INASGOC (\u1ee6y ban Olympic Indonesia) ch\u01b0a th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o g\u00ec v\u1ec1 bu\u1ed5i b\u1ed1c th\u0103m. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u0103n b\u1ea3n n\u00e0o t\u1eeb ph\u00eda nh\u00e0 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft v\u00e0o tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft l\u00e0 bu\u1ed5i b\u1ed1c th\u0103m ng\u00e0y 5/7 \u0111\u00e3 xong nh\u01b0ng v\u00ec 2 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00ean ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u1edd. Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i hay kh\u00f4ng v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o l\u00e0 quy\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a OCA v\u00e0 INASGOC\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1ea1i Indonesia cho r\u1eb1ng l\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Nam ASIAD s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 Hai t\u1edbi, tuy nhi\u00ean n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t kh\u1ea3 thi v\u00e0 h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n b\u1ed1c th\u0103m \u0111\u01b0a 2 \u0111\u1ed9i UAE v\u00e0 Palestine v\u00e0o 2 b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3. T\u1ee9c l\u00e0 c\u00f3 2 b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1ebd c\u00f3 5 \u0111\u1ed9i, 2 \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 nh\u00ec c\u00f9ng 4 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u1ea1ng 3 c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t s\u1ebd v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"L\u0110B\u0110 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 AFC n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i ASIAD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"L\u0110B\u0110 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 AFC n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i ASIAD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/ldbd-chau-a-muon-boc-tham-lai-mon-bong-da-nam-asiad.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u1eb1m chung b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018.</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span class=\"apple-converted-space\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1510","checkdouble":"191785"},{"date":"15:17 22/07","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP TPHCM vs Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh 19h00 ng\u00e0y 22/7 (V-League 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/22/tphcm-vs-quang-ninh-vong-20-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><